{"tid":2175310,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"28歲男警太子站偷拍女督察裙底","createTime":"2020-08-26T11:40:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T17:02:33.000Z","uid":219379,"like":365,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":102,"replies":[{"pid":"fe14811fd97e4767cab240877df90d19c1e6757c","tid":2175310,"uid":219379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:40:55.000Z","msg":"港鐵太子站發生偷拍裙底事件，昨日(25日)傍晚6時許，一名男子疑在上址扶手電梯，以手提電話偷拍一名37歲的女子裙底，被對方當場揭發。警員接報到場，經初步調查，以涉嫌遊蕩拘捕該名姓吳(28歲)男子，並揭發他為一名休班警員，帶署扣查。據了解，事主為一名女督察。<br />\n<br />\n案件現交由旺角警區重案組跟進，吳已獲准保釋侯查，須於9月下旬向警方報到。警方強調，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，定必嚴正處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/28-%E6%AD%B2%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E7%94%B7%E8%AD%A6%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99%E5%81%B7%E6%8B%8D%E5%A5%B3%E7%9D%A3%E5%AF%9F%E8%A3%99%E5%BA%95-%E9%81%AD%E8%B8%A2%E7%88%86%E7%95%B6%E5%A0%B4%E5%B0%B1%E9%80%AE-071916297.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F28-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25AB%2599%25E5%2581%25B7%25E6%258B%258D%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%259D%25A3%25E5%25AF%259F%25E8%25A3%2599%25E5%25BA%2595-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25B8%25A2%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E9%2580%25AE-071916297.html&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatqC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=803ea50d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/28-%E6%AD%B2%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E7%94%B7%E8%AD%A6%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99%E5%81%B7%E6%8B%8D%E5%A5%B3%E7%9D%A3%E5%AF%9F%E8%A3%99%E5%BA%95-%E9%81%AD%E8%B8%A2%E7%88%86%E7%95%B6%E5%A0%B4%E5%B0%B1%E9%80%AE-071916297.html</a>"},{"pid":"5308f2dd22e13c140edff3a2084c0e524d38d0d8","tid":2175310,"uid":159313,"like":141,"dislike":0,"score":141,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:42:00.000Z","msg":"28歲睇37歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c50aeadedba4f862cc6be67e91e3f96dfb25a0","tid":2175310,"uid":132128,"like":70,"dislike":0,"score":70,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08